name: Unexpected Frappuccino Occurrences
description:
Make the alien happy, you heard that they drink their coffee sweet!

But horrible chickens want to get your sugar! Will you be able to drop the sugar in the cup?

Move with the Arrow Keys, but be careful, your UFO is kinda... broken

- TEAM INSULINE at the Kolibri Game Jam-

Generalist and Producer: Luca Lombardo

Art: Daria Kutepowa, Lara Rogonja

Programming:Lara Paul, Tonio Suessdorf
